---
config:
  theme: dark
  layout: dagre
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant DM as Faster R-CNN
    participant CM as ResNet50
    participant FS as File Storage

    U->>API: POST /api/analyze-batch (files[])
    API->>API: Extract device fingerprint
    API->>DB: Get/Create User
    DB-->>API: User record
    API->>DB: Create ScanBatch (PROCESSING)
    DB-->>API: batch_id

    loop For each image file
        API->>FS: Save image
        FS-->>API: storage_path
        API->>DB: Create ScanImage
        API->>API: Convert to RGB
        API->>DM: detect_seeds(image)
        DM-->>API: boxes[], scores[]
        
        loop For each detected seed
            API->>CM: classify(crop)
            CM-->>API: probability
            API->>DB: Create SeedDetection
        end
    end

    API->>API: Aggregate statistics
    API->>DB: Update ScanBatch (COMPLETED)
    API-->>U: JSON response
